        "description": "You're a master of reading and manipulating others - saying just the right thing to get them to do what you want, while letting them think it was their idea all along. And you're more than just a charmer - you've got a well-rounded skill set, capable of shooting your way out of a jam, or melting into shadows to avoid one in the first place. But you really shine when the spotlight's on you - whether it's talking your way into a facility while decked out in the perfect disguise, or squeezing every last nuyen out of Mr. Johnson before the deal's done.\n\nKeep your Skill Mastery talents in mind - whenever you make a Con or Influence test, you score a critical hit if both of your Crit Dice are a 5 or a 6 (not just if they're both 6's)."
